data.title: Hairzoo Webster, Empire Blvd
data.text: Hairzoo offers a professional team of stylists that are eager to help you look and feel your best. Visit Hairzoo for a stylish haircut, color or one of our other salon services for men, women, seniors and children. Hairzoo specializes in a wide range of services that include haircuts, color, highlights, lowlights, ombre hair color, blowouts, updos, perms, extensions, braids, facial waxing, and our invigorating Tea Tree Experience. Hairzoo stylists will also advise on a wide variety of professional hair care products and tools. Our stylists are ready to exceed your expectations by providing you with the Hairzoo Ultimate Guest Experience. Find us off Empire Blvd near the Plank Road intersection. We are located down the street from Wegmans Eastway and Walmart, on the same side of the street as the Delta Sonic. Whether you walk right in or schedule a reservation, we look forward to welcoming you to Hairzoo. Call 585-671-6131 today. Hairzoo, the hair experts. Open 7 days a week, just walk-in!
